icle/.premium/biden-says-two-state-solution-must-follow-israel-hamas-war-slams-extremist-settlers/0000018b-6838-d78a-a5eb-7cbb32020000</link><description>在迄今为止对战争最广泛的评论中，美国总统还质疑哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部的伤亡数字，并敦促继续与沙特阿拉伯进行谈判</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 19:33:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/biden-says-two-state-solution-must-follow-israel-hamas-war-slams-extremist-settlers/0000018b-6838-d78a-a5eb-7cbb32020000</guid></item><item><title>新众议院议长迈克·约翰逊是一位福音派基督徒，与以色列极右翼分子有联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/new-house-speaker-mike-johnson-an-evangelical-christian-holds-ties-to-israels-far-right/0000018b-67b3-db57-a7cb-efbf8a8d0000</link><description>路易斯安那州众议员迈克·约翰逊 (Mike Johnson) 将他 2020 年对耶路撒冷圣殿山的访问描述为“圣经预言的实现”；他的当选是华盛顿福音派迄今为止最重大的胜利</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 17:56:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/new-house-speaker-mike-johnson-an-evangelical-christian-holds-ties-to-israels-far-right/0000018b-67b3-db57-a7cb-efbf8a8d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称，哈马斯一半以上人质拥有外国公民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/more-than-half-of-hamas-hostages-have-foreign-citizenship-israel-says/0000018b-67be-d78a-a5eb-7fbf08360000</link><description>以色列政府称，138名人质持有外国护照，其中包括15名阿根廷人、12名德国人、12名美国人、6名法国人和6名俄罗斯人</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 17:45:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/more-than-half-of-hamas-hostages-have-foreign-citizenship-israel-says/0000018b-67be-d78a-a5eb-7fbf08360000</guid></item><item><title>“我们现在都需要治疗”：特拉维夫画廊为战争提供喘息空间</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-all-need-therapy-now-the-tel-aviv-gallery-offering-breathing-space-from-the-war/0000018b-6722-d979-a3bb-ef77d3650000</link><description>“菌丝体”是一个与众不同的装置：部分是艺术体验，部分是治疗诊所——它的时机再合适不过了。艺术家莎朗·格拉兹伯格 (Sharon Glazberg) 表示，“这个空间仿佛就是为此而生”</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 17:40:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-all-need-therapy-now-the-tel-aviv-gallery-offering-breathing-space-from-the-war/0000018b-6722-d979-a3bb-ef77d3650000</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，以色列推迟入侵加沙，以便美国加强中东地区的防御</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-delaying-gaza-invasion-so-u-s-can-bolster-defenses-across-mideast-wsj-reports/0000018b-6783-d326-a39b-679bc63f0000</link><description>报道称，以色列将推迟行动，直到美国加强中东地区的防御。然而，美国官员进一步担心人质谈判和人道主义危机的影响</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 17:29:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-delaying-gaza-invasion-so-u-s-can-bolster-defenses-across-mideast-wsj-reports/0000018b-6783-d326-a39b-679bc63f0000</guid></item><item><title>捷克和奥地利领导人访问以色列承诺声援哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/visiting-israel-leaders-of-czech-republic-austria-pledge-solidarity-against-hamas/0000018b-6763-d979-a3bb-ef77992a0000</link><description>捷克总理彼得·菲亚拉称哈马斯为“共同的敌人”，奥地利总理卡尔·内哈默在与以色列总理和总统的会晤中谈到“共同打击恐怖主义”</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 16:07:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/visiting-israel-leaders-of-czech-republic-austria-pledge-solidarity-against-hamas/0000018b-6763-d979-a3bb-ef77992a0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯正在考验以色列的“特氟龙经济”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/hamas-is-putting-israels-teflon-economy-to-the-test/0000018b-675d-d979-a3bb-ef7f51e50000</link><description>标准普尔、穆迪和惠誉尚未准备好降低以色列的信用评级，但战争才刚刚开始。如果他们这样做的话会发生什么？</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 15:20:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/hamas-is-putting-israels-teflon-economy-to-the-test/0000018b-675d-d979-a3bb-ef7f51e50000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击后以色列境外犹太人的恐惧和创伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-fear-and-trauma-of-jews-outside-israel-after-the-hamas-attacks/0000018b-66be-db57-a7cb-eebf2e530000</link><description>今天，作为一名在伦敦的犹太人，我感受到了以前从未经历过的恐惧。世界各地的犹太社区正在努力应对 10 月 7 日的创伤以及对当天野蛮行径的可悲反应</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 14:12:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-fear-and-trauma-of-jews-outside-israel-after-the-hamas-attacks/0000018b-66be-db57-a7cb-eebf2e530000</guid></item><item><title>约旦女王声称媒体和国际社会对以色列和巴勒斯坦死亡问题采取“双重标准”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/jordans-queen-claims-double-standard-regarding-israeli-palestinian-deaths/0000018b-66d8-d1c5-af9f-77fb74c20000</link><description>在接受美国有线电视新闻网采访时，约旦女王拉尼娅谴责西方对加沙的偏见，称有关“以色列儿童在基布兹被屠杀”的报道未经证实</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 13:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/jordans-queen-claims-double-standard-regarding-israeli-palestinian-deaths/0000018b-66d8-d1c5-af9f-77fb74c20000</guid></item><item><title>美国各地校园计划举行罢工抗议“加沙种族灭绝”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/walkouts-protesting-gaza-genocide-planned-on-campuses-across-u-s/0000018b-66b9-d326-a39b-66b9b8130000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击事件以来，美国校园的紧张局势已升级至前所未有的水平，该事件造成 1,400 名以色列人死亡、220 人被囚禁，而在以色列对袭击作出反应后，加沙有超过 6,500 名巴勒斯坦人死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 12:40:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/walkouts-protesting-gaza-genocide-planned-on-campuses-across-u-s/0000018b-66b9-d326-a39b-66b9b8130000</guid></item><item><title>“即使在战争之前，加沙的水也不足以淋浴”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-discourse-of-revenge-dehumanizes-an-entire-population/0000018b-6645-d2a9-afeb-667d5e5e0000</link><description>哈佛大学讲师马尔基特·肖山 (Malkit Shoshan) 20 年来一直在研究中东冲突地区，其中包括加沙。她说，尽管很痛苦，但现在是讨论结束冲突的解决方案的时候了。她说，“复仇的言论使整个人口丧失了人性”</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 12:39:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-discourse-of-revenge-dehumanizes-an-entire-population/0000018b-6645-d2a9-afeb-667d5e5e0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔总理希望加沙“很快”取得突破；以色列官员赞扬多哈的“重要”努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/qatar-hopes-for-gaza-hostage-breakthrough-soon-israel-lauds-dohas-essential-efforts/0000018b-6695-db57-a7cb-ee9f18e60000</link><description>有报道称卡塔尔与哈马斯进行谈判以释放大量以色列和外国人质，以色列领导人呼吁这个“窝藏并资助哈马斯领导人”的海湾国家对该恐怖组织施加影响</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 12:33:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/qatar-hopes-for-gaza-hostage-breakthrough-soon-israel-lauds-dohas-essential-efforts/0000018b-6695-db57-a7cb-ee9f18e60000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼、仇视同性恋的以色列联盟议员调整政府预算以援助以色列加沙边境社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/far-right-coalition-mk-redirects-govt-budget-to-aid-israeli-gaza-border-communities/0000018b-6682-d326-a39b-669acc190000</link><description>毛兹与其他一些联盟议员一样，鉴于与哈马斯的持续战争而选择牺牲预算，他们认为，在“整个以色列民族都在与残酷的敌人作战”之际，这是必要的举动。反对我们&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 11:49:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/far-right-coalition-mk-redirects-govt-budget-to-aid-israeli-gaza-border-communities/0000018b-6682-d326-a39b-669acc190000</guid></item><item><title>“我把孩子们的名字写在他们的身上。至少他们会在埋葬前辨认出他们的身份”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-wrote-my-childrens-names-on-their-bodies-at-least-theyll-identify/0000018b-6640-d8ab-a3eb-6f6a6d3d0000</link><description>警告：图形内容。 “他们告诉我们这里更安全，但轰炸无处不在。昨天他们炸毁了附近的一座建筑物。夜晚非常困难&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 11:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-wrote-my-childrens-names-on-their-bodies-at-least-theyll-identify/0000018b-6640-d8ab-a3eb-6f6a6d3d0000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其埃尔多安称哈马斯是“解放组织”，而不是恐怖分子，并取消对以色列的访问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/turkeys-erdogan-says-hamas-is-liberation-group-not-terrorists-cancels-israel-visit/0000018b-663f-d8ab-a3eb-6f7fd1550000</link><description>在向议会发表的讲话中，土耳其领导人要求以色列停止在约旦河西岸的“定居恐怖”和对加沙的袭击，表示巴勒斯坦人应该“团结起来”实现两国解决方案，并表示西方应该停止“火上浇油”。火&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 11:03:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/turkeys-erdogan-says-hamas-is-liberation-group-not-terrorists-cancels-israel-visit/0000018b-663f-d8ab-a3eb-6f7fd1550000</guid></item><item><title>“做内塔尼亚胡”将意味着走上自杀之路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/doing-a-netanyahu-will-mean-pursuing-a-suicidal-path/0000018b-664f-d473-a5fb-66cf35010000</link><description>目前尚不清楚为什么西方领导人愿意与本杰明·内塔尼亚胡总理这样的人合作</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 10:54:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/doing-a-netanyahu-will-mean-pursuing-a-suicidal-path/0000018b-664f-d473-a5fb-66cf35010000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争促使意识形态上对立的以色列团体共同努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gaza-war-pushes-ideologically-opposed-israeli-groups-to-work-together/0000018b-65f5-d473-a5fb-65fd7f130000</link><description>在 2023 年的大部分时间里，反司法政变组织“武装兄弟姐妹”与极端正统派团体以及内塔尼亚胡政府中代表他们的政客几乎陷入了内战。加沙战争使双方团结起来共同对抗新的敌人</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 10:47:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gaza-war-pushes-ideologically-opposed-israeli-groups-to-work-together/0000018b-65f5-d473-a5fb-65fd7f130000</guid></item></channel></rss>